    "description": "The Imamura Securities Co., Ltd. provides investment and financial services in Japan. The company engages in the buying and selling of securities, market derivative transactions, and foreign market derivative transactions; intermediation, brokerage, and agency for the purchase and sale of securities, as well as entrustment of the buying and selling of securities on financial instruments exchange markets; securities underwriting; public offering and private placement of securities; secondary offering of securities; handling of public offerings, secondary offerings, and private placements; and discretionary investment contract intermediation services. It also provides iRoot, an online stock trading service; stocks; futures and options; investment trusts; bonds; NISA; shareholder community; discretionary investment management; tax account consultation; and agent services. In addition, the company offers financing, asset management, insurance, and other services. The Imamura Securities Co., Ltd. was founded in 1920 and is headquartered in Kanazawa, Japan."
